Hello! This is Walter Ross from Aquidneck Yacht Brokers. How can I assist you today?

Hello, I'm Rebecca Coleman. I’m surprised! I wasn't expecting to receive this call.

Hi Rebecca, nice to meet you! We like to ensure our customers have the best experience. Could I start by confirming your phone number, just to make sure we have the right details on file?

Sure, my phone number is five five five, one two three, four five six seven.

Thank you, Rebecca. Additionally, could you please confirm your email address too?

Yes, it's rebecca dot coleman at email dot com.

Got it, thank you! Now, is there anything specific I can help you with regarding your yacht inquiries?

Actually, I was curious about the process of listing a yacht with your brokerage.

I'd be happy to guide you through that. We start with an appraisal and take it from there. I'll email you detailed information on the process.

Thank you for your time, Rebecca. If you have further questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
